dc_title_s: Iberian Peninsula 1:250,000: Leiria, sheet 47. Series A.M.S. M581
dc_description_s: United States. Army Map Service. North Decimal Degree 40.0000. South Decimal Degree 39.0000. East Decimal Degree -8.0000. West Decimal Degree -9.0000. Alternate title: Leiria, Portugal. Polyconic projection. With Portuguese-English glossary. Relief shown by 100 m. contour interval, gradient tint and spot heights. Standard map series designation: A.M.S. M581. "Compiled from Portugal, Servicos Geodesicos, 1900-38; Portugal, 100,000 Instituto Geofico, 1937; Portugal, 100,000 Servicos Geodesicos, 1866-1881; Portugal, 1:250,000, Estandor Maior do Exercito, 1937, 1938; Road Map of Spain and Portugal, 1:400,000, A.M.S., sheet 46, Third Edition, 1943; Railways of Spain and Portugal 1:1,500,000, G.S.G.S., 1941, corrected from Intelligence Reports, 1942-44. Partially revised from aerial photography, 1941.".
